<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs></opener>
   <p><lb/><subst><del><gap/></del><add>B</add></subst>inas a te accepi humanissimas <rs key="B_1717-06-03_991170517039305501" type="letters">litteras</rs>
<lb/>quibus me certiorem facere dignatus es
         <lb/>Vir <abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">e</hi></abbr> de tuo discessu ita ut
         <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs> profecturus sis prope <date when="1717-06-13">festum
            <lb/><choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Divi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118503510" type="person">Antonii</rs></date>. Tibi gratias ago maximas
         <lb/>tibique significo quod hodierna die
      <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-2643743" type="place">Londinum</rs> transmitto tuam <rs key="B_1717-05-31_991170517018205501" type="letter">episto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lam</rs> pro <abbr>D.</abbr> Equite <rs key="pers_DE-588-118587544" type="person">Isaaco Newto<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>no</rs>. Antequam <del>istinc </del>isthinc disce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>das mittam ad te <rs key="B_1716-06-06_991170515017605501" type="letter">litteras</rs> pro <abbr>Illust.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr>
<lb/><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruo</rs> tuo quem su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> diligo
         <lb/>ac magni facio. </p><closer>Tu interim vale
         <lb/>sciasque me esse ad mandata tua
            <lb/>paratissimum.</closer>
